  "body": "### Description\n\nHi team,\r\n\r\ndo you have any plans to upgrade snakeyaml version to address CVE-2022-1471? It is used by following quarkus components:\r\n\r\n- io.quarkus-config-yaml : 2.16.12.final\r\n- io.quarkus : quarkus-smallrye-openapi : 2.16.12.final\r\n\r\nI know it is mainly used to parse secure inputs such as application.yml, but it will help to calm down security officers as this CVE is flaged with highest security  score in my project.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nLooks like version 2.x addressed this CVE:\r\nhttps://bitbucket.org/snakeyaml/snakeyaml/wiki/Changes",
